thread.title: Myanmar urged not to drag out case against Reuters reporters

title: Myanmar urged not to drag out case against Reuters reporters
text:
Myanmar urged not to drag out case against Reuters reporters 4:30pm GMT - 00:52 
International observers urge Myanmar not to drag out legal proceedings against two Reuters journalists accused of possessing secret government papers. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
